U-Hexen is yet another port of Hexen, popular game from Raven Softrware to
Simple Directmedia Layer (SDL) library.
It works on Linux, FreeBSD, OpenBSD and Windows, and can be ported to other platforms.

Code and ideas is taken from various versions of hexen, heretic and doom.

Please report bugs to me by e-mail svm@asu.ru, or by ICQ# 17541775.

